{"tid":1304473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求求你地班港豬醒下啦！五大訴求先係真正目標","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:09:37.000Z","uid":34296,"like":69,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"852c48c52677ac8aec3e599acd976c7faf9eb939","tid":1304473,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得梁烈士犧牲原因！？<br />\n<br />\n全面撒回送中！<br />\n<br />\n佢既遺願其實未達成架！<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好focus 乜撚野連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞反黑警活動，反藍絲活動，各區遊行<br />\n<br />\n係到哂氣哂力，政府搞咁多野就係想分化香港人<br />\n<br />\n所以咪由班廢老走出黎拆牆囉<br />\n<br />\n佢地拆牆就由佢地拆啦<br />\n<br />\n最重要係爭取撒回修訂逃犯條例！實行雙普選！先係最急切性！<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地班港豬唔好咁善忘得唔得！<br />\n<br />\n今次個運動真係就黎壽終正寢架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共仲要整多個智慧燈柱，計分制<br />\n<br />\n港共又即刻割地比班解防軍<br />\n<br />\n你地班港豬就係到護牆on99<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心見到為左個油塘連儂牆係到同班廢老嘈就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b4e3238dd3837e3de108d4f8b34dbf0c88eb75","tid":1304473,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:26:18.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"f812b11c48f3faa225f63f02e4ad590bc187874b","tid":1304473,"uid":34296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"推到所有on9港豬都睇到！"},{"pid":"3e2a6498c6220d1f4573cee8104be12efadcf8a1","tid":1304473,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"On9港豬訓醒未"},{"pid":"fb0c0ce73d42f2facfe5e5ffc5b6967c3efcba2e","tid":1304473,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"推推推！"},{"pid":"c1caa50b7cfde00f96210bfa1489ceeb0b79e423","tid":1304473,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"醒下啦港豬"},{"pid":"52a3157b44079f4ec3aa026e45c771b64869c4e7","tid":1304473,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa